form.custom-apply-form.m-auto.max-w-sm.elevation.p-2.md_p-3(method="POST", action="https://docsearch-hub.herokuapp.com/form/inbound", id="apply")
  .custom-form-content.form-content
    .mb-2.form-step(name="step-documentationUrl")
      label.control-label(for="documentationUrl") Documentation URL
      input#url.form-control(name="documentationUrl", placeholder="https://project.org/docs", type="url", required)  
      p.form-hint.text-grey-1.text--1.leading-2.my-1.italic We'll crawl pages at this address and index the content on Algolia.
      p.form-error.text-mars-2.text--1.my-1.bold

    .mb-2.form-step(name="step-githubUrl")
      label.control-label(for="githubUrl") 
        |Repository url
        .inline.text--1.text-grey-1  (optional)
      input#url.form-control(name="githubUrl", placeholder="https://github.com/username/project", type="url", required)  
      p.form-hint.text-grey-1.text--1.leading-2.my-1.italic This is optional, but we'll give higher priority to open source requests
      p.form-error.text-mars-2.text--1.my-1.bold

    .mb-2.form-step(name="step-email")
      label.control-label(for="email") Email
      input#email.form-control(name="email", placeholder="you@project.org", type="email", required)
      p.form-hint.text-grey-1.text--1.leading-2.my-1.italic We'll send you the JavaScript snippet you'll have to integrate into your documentation.
      p.form-error.text-mars-2.text--1.my-1.bold

      .hidden
        div.g-recaptcha(data-sitekey=placeholders.recaptchaKey, data-badge="inline", data-callback="recaptchaCallback", data-size="invisible")


    .mb-2.form-step(name="step-algoliaPolicy")
      label.cursor-pointer
        input(name="algoliaPolicy", type="checkbox", required)
        span
          |  I'm the 
          .bold.inline owner
          |  of the website and I 
          a(href="./who-can-apply.html") read the checklist
        |  before applying.
      p.form-error.text-mars-2.text--1.bold.my-1

    .mb-2
    button.c-button.c-button-primary.w-100(type="submit") Apply to DocSearch
    p.leading-2.text-1.my-1 
      | This form is using reCaptcha as a spam protection measure (see 
      a.clickable(href="https://policies.google.com/privacy") Privacy
      |, 
      a.clickable(href="https://policies.google.com/terms") Terms
      |). Refer to 
      a.clickable(href="https://www.algolia.com/policies/terms") Algolia's Privacy Policy
      |  for more information on how we use and protect your data.



  .custom-form-thank-you.hidden
    .poppins.text-4.mb-2 Thank you!
    p.text-2.leading-2.mb-1 Your request will be processed by our team. 
    p.text-2.leading-2.mb-1
      |We'll get back to you on 
      span.custom-placeholder-email.inline.text-nebula your email
      |  with the snippet of JavaScript you'll need to integrate into 
      span.custom-placeholder-url.inline.text-nebula your website
      |.
    p.text-2.leading-2  Please be patient, it can take a few days.

  .custom-form-recaptcha-fallback.hidden
    .poppins.text-4.mb-2 Oops!
    p.text-2.leading-2.mb-1 It seems that our form is not working correctly right now. 
    p.text-2.leading-2.mb-1
      | But don't worry, you can still send an email directly to 
      a.clickable(href="mailto:docsearch@algolia.com") docsearch@algolia.com
      |  with your website url and GitHub repo address to apply.
    p.text-2.leading-2  Sorry for the inconvenience!

script(src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js", async, defer)
